title: Tesla Full Self-Driving Subscription & Google Pixel 6 Breakdown
description:
This week, Marques and Andrew discuss the new Tesla full self-driving subscription model and if they think it's actually worth it. Then, David Imel joins the podcast to discuss Google's new Tensor processor and what implications it will have for both the Pixel 6 and the future of Google.
